snippet.title: Amber Heard accused of 'attacking sister' after a video emerges in court,Depp is in silent!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard 's sister Whitney Henriquez has been accused of lying in court when she said the actress had never been violent towards her after a video emerged today.

Heard's ex-husband Johnny Depp, 57, is suing News Group Newspapers for libel over a story published in The Sun in 2018 which branded him a "wife beater" .
